Class DTraceReader

  • Object
    • DeclReader
      • DTraceReader

  • public class DTraceReader
extends DeclReader
    Reads dtrace files and provides methods to access the information within them. A dtrace file contains both declarations and data.

    Do not use this program as an example of how to read a dtrace file. The better way to do that is to define a FileIO.Processor and pass it to FileIO.read_data_trace_files(Collection, PptMap, daikon.FileIO.Processor, boolean).
